{"tid":1019343,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"有無人鍾意蘇打綠/青峰？","createTime":"2019-02-13T01:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T16:09:15.000Z","uid":214581,"like":19,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a81978ff51b2cc93d097b22a98e0305aa71d9859","tid":1019343,"uid":214581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:02:11.000Z","msg":"留意左呢隊台灣band好耐 學生時期已經成日聽老豆播佢地啲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無眠 我好想你 小時候 小情歌 下雨的夜晚  你被寫在我的歌裡 好多歌都係聽一兩次就入晒腦<br />\n到依家蘇打綠解散 佢參加左個大陸節目《歌手2019》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4o0BD1KUL5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4o0BD1KUL5g&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwifsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=1ad87220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4o0BD1KUL5g</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MeZb6o0VE7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMeZb6o0VE7w&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwifsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=2da96a2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MeZb6o0VE7w</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Jd4eYeaogtI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJd4eYeaogtI&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwifsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=b66efb8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Jd4eYeaogtI</a><br />\nsorry for殘體字但佢live真係好撚正 尤其是高音<br />\n雖然始終覺得我們都係eason唱得有feel啲 但翻唱嚟講青峰都做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽親佢啲歌都覺得好舒服好療癒 有冇人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f159103c5d6c16aaeed734fcfc19d3ebbe00268","tid":1019343,"uid":229955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:03:42.000Z","msg":"走啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ba4829ec36018f15e285e00912e3661e475d0a","tid":1019343,"uid":214581,"like"